## Limitations

The findings are based on secondary data from online sources, which may not capture all nuances of employee turnover. The reasons for job resignation can vary widely across industries, regions, and individual circumstances, which may not be fully represented in the sources reviewed. Additionally, the data is subject to the publication dates of the articles, which may not reflect the most current trends in employee turnover.